{"tid":2352941,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Tesla真係好嗎？今日盤前有點唏噓，唉。","createTime":"2021-01-04T11:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T09:46:50.000Z","uid":37146,"like":31,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5c3aed056e5da164b04e48fd12446401ad7e0b8a","tid":2352941,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T11:00:34.000Z","msg":"近年電動車發展迅速，某啲城市已經公布左，2030年起禁售汽油車及柴油車，甚至係全面禁止燃油車上路<br />\n其實成件事係好近，好快到<br />\n唉，我就係到諗，咁到時勞斯萊斯，法拉利，或者係啲好有歷史價值既牌子（例如某啲日本車牌子）就慢慢會消失<br />\n佢地其實係代表住一啲文化：尊貴，奢華，舒服，做工，加速力，歷史價值，駕駛技術，以往賽場上既一啲往績，財富象徵等等<br />\n雖然我對超跑，或者高級牌子既車冇乜大既興趣，可能係我未有錢啦，但係會覺得可惜既就係，好似見到一種動物品種，話俾你知道9年後就要絕種既個種感覺<br />\n呢種係一樣代表人類既文化，9年後就要慢慢消失？真係有啲唏噓<br />\n<br />\n而電動車就係代表，安靜，方便，環保，做工差，唔需要駕駛技術（自由駕駛揸都唔洗你揸），行走既電腦，人類既進步等等<br />\n<br />\n當然明白世界要進步，同埋燃油車係對環境既損害嚴重，所以電動車一定係大勢所趨，心情有點複雜......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">最後想講，今日盤前TSLA又升到仆街，開心到跳舞</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48cfc46ddb5714be13a2af422135f2e587f3ae1","tid":2352941,"uid":104371,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T11:06:15.000Z","msg":"703走左呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚又要不問價入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b138998b7090d67573d6ad60225fe02e825283b","tid":2352941,"uid":37146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e48cfc46ddb5714be13a2af422135f2e587f3ae1","tid":2352941,"uid":104371,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T11:06:15.000Z","msg":"703走左呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚又要不問價入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T11:07:43.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">柒</span></span>"},{"pid":"4906365a14163fa4300c82d41268a48c8cb193dd","tid":2352941,"uid":118520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e48cfc46ddb5714be13a2af422135f2e587f3ae1","tid":2352941,"uid":104371,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T11:06:15.000Z","msg":"703走左呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚又要不問價入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T11:08:27.000Z","msg":"晤sh正儍仔"},{"pid":"ad9ff4d42b8d3563dd3b2ddc3dcf2204246d2a42","tid":2352941,"uid":104371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4906365a14163fa4300c82d41268a48c8cb193dd","tid":2352941,"uid":118520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e48cfc46ddb5714be13a2af422135f2e587f3ae1","tid":2352941,"uid":104371,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T1